data.description: . . 8 years Young,   Spacious 4 bedroom 2.5 bathrooms home in Gated Community.  Enter into an Awesome OPEN floor plan with high ceilings. The Living room/Dining room has nice windows to give natural light. The Kitchen has a gas stove, wrap around Granite Island, stainless appliances and Huge walk-in Pantry.  There is a convenient Half Bath for Guest off the Foyer. The Primary Bedroom/Bathroom suite is located Downstairs towards the back of the home. It offers soaring tray ceiling, Bathroom with dual Vanities, separate Shower, a garden/soaking Tub & a large Walk-in closet.  On the 2nd level enter a large common area that can be used as an office or media room.  There are also 3 additional large bedrooms on level 2. Back Patio has a nice view of the Lake. . . This is a community with a POOL, Fitness center, and Clubhouse. . . .  DID Not Flood!  GATED . . . . get CODE for Gate!
